parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, compromising the safety of the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The airbag light stays on
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
the airbag deploys partially or with reduced inflation
the airbag sensor malfunctions
the driver's seat belt does not lock up upon impact.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning airbag sensor can cause the airbag to deploy unnecessarily or fail to deploy in a crash, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light stays on
the airbag sensor malfunctions
the airbag deploys partially or with reduced inflation
the airbag does not deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Improper airbag deployment can cause injuries or fatalities, compromising the safety of the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The airbag deploys partially or with reduced inflation
the airbag causes burns or scrapes
the airbag dust comes out but does not inflate
the airbag deployment causes severe head and neck injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature engine failure can lead to sudden loss of power, stalling, and increased risk of accidents, as well as costly repairs and potential engine replacement.
symptoms: White smoke emanating from the vehicle
engine failure
engine replacement required
premature wear on engine components (e.g.
rings
head gasket).

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt can lead to increased risk of injury or death in the event of an accident, as the occupant may not be properly restrained.
symptoms: The seat belt fails to restrain the occupant during an accident
the seat belt does not retract
the seat belt is inoperative
the occupant suffers injuries due to seat belt failure.
